  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ハードコアを基にしたアフターマーケットリリースで、かつてセガによってリリースのライセンスが取得されていたが、元のパブリッシャーであるサイグノシスによって未発売となった。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Hardcore finally awakes.\n\nExcept for a few people, no one has ever seen or played this gem. But thanks to friends and our wonderful ‘A-Team’, the original data has finally been recovered. So after nearly 25 years of deep sleep, Hardcore will finally be published in 2019 under the name Ultracore!\n\nUltracore is being developed using original Sega Mega Drive development hardware. It will then be ported to run on modern platforms. We intend to finish the game the way it was meant to be played!\n\nEverything is being handled with care, to guarantee gamers get the best possible version of this masterpiece.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
  "first_release_date": "2019-03-25",
